name: **Illannambraher**
description: Illannambraher L922-942 Sheet 30/31 Lovely island, waisted near the W end, the smaller further W end being the more intensively farmed, and even fenced. There is a shingle beach for landing either side of the waist. Portaging ? Both ends are grazed and both are pleasant. Damsons grow in profusion.
